    Choir of The King's Consort

  13. No. 13, Recit. But Let My Due Feet Never Fail (Il Penseroso)
    Robert King

  14. No. 14, Chorus. There Let the Pealing Organ Blow (Il Penseroso)
    Choir of The King's Consort

  15. No. 15, Air. May at Last My Weary Age (Il Penseroso)
    Robert King

